parameters:
Hmm... You're a beginner adventurer, right? Your footsteps
really give off a total amateur vibe... I'll secretly teach
you a thing or two.

Actually, even if you wipe out in a regular battle, it won't
be an instant game over. It's quite forgiving, so go ahead
and keep going!

Well, it's not like you give off a dangerous vibe or
anything...!

Oh... That's right. If it becomes too difficult and
bothersome, it's better to just change the difficulty level!

Difficulty level can be changed from the Options in the
Menu. I said it properly, you know! If it's too much to
handle, it's better to just lower it!

By changing the difficulty level from the Options, you can
alter the balance of battles. If you're not good at or
unfamiliar with RPGs, please choose Easy.

For those who don't want to battle... We have prepared an
even easier difficulty level called Sweet. If necessary,
please feel free to use it.

...There is a possibility of unreasonable balance in high
difficulty levels. I would be grateful if you could enjoy it
in a good way.

Sorry for rambling on. Well then, take care and have a safe
journey.

Isn't the BGM here not good? I really like it, you know... I
could listen to it forever...

In battle, self-enhancement is important! Strengthen
yourself and deal massive damage!... Written on a signboard,
there is some doodle.

Don't be noisy...! We just hit with physical attacks without
thinking...! Right, everyone...!... is written.
